div.head:
285. Telegram From the Embassy in Guyana to the Department of StateSource: Carter Library, National Security
                        Affairs, Staff Material, North/South, Pastor, Country, Box 24, Folder: Guyana, 1/77–12/78. Secret;
                        Stadis; Exdis.

div.p:
(A) Burnham wanted this appointment to
                    precede a visit which he had planned during 1978 to the USSR, other Eastern European countries and North
                    Korea;
